title: Big Sean Shares Video for 'I Decided' Single "Moves"
text:
Late last month, Big Sean formally announced his next official studio album and introduced the effort by releasing its lead single, "Moves." To begin the new year, the superstar rapper is sharing the visual for his latest major record and the follow-up to his last video for "Bounce Back." The clip for "Moves" comes to us courtesy of director Mike Carson and producers Austin Barbera & Taylor Vandegrift; like many of the Detroit rapper's recent visuals, it's straightforward and keeps the focus on Sean.
You can check out the vignette for Big Sean's "Moves" above -- the Detroit rapper's new album I Decided is set to arrive on February 3.
Read more at Hypebeast.com
